      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EVEN BACKWARDS (1) is a classy pup building a strong winning record at the journey. Has quickly put herself into the picture to win the last couple of runs. Scored latest at this track in a handy 18.11. Boasts three wins from four starts out of this box. Can measure up again. ZERO CONTROL (2) tackled far tougher grade latest but ran very well to hit the frame when 3rd (18.42) at this track in Grade 3. Won an easier race the start before that at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Boasts a strong record from this draw with four wins and four minor placings from nine starts. Expected to feature. LITTLE RILEY (4) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, half a length from the winner Trust Me (18.30) at this track. Will give a great sight again. TERRITORY LIFE (7) can measure up with the right run.",
